  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to explore whether a chatbot based on NLP techniques has better&#xD;
      educational effect than printed booklets on knowledge of COVID-19 and its vaccination. The&#xD;
      chatbot was built based on large language models and reinforcement learning with human&#xD;
      feedback, and could generate ChatGPT-level responses.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
